{"tid":2119474,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(心態決定境界) 無錯 一定要鬥黃 但只可以同自己鬥","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T09:58:31.000Z","uid":4322,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"12b87d1f9c801d91b78d26925598775d222cecba","tid":2119474,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"無錯 只係同自己鬥黃 唔好同任何其他人鬥黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdaCeXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdaCeXT.jpg&h=a191af16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單講 你可以統計下每日幫襯幾多黃店<br />\n自己set目標去「進步」<br />\n例如每日一餐 可唔可以每日兩餐？<br />\n中間搭過下午茶 宵夜又得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又例如除左食飯 衣住行又可唔可以都選擇用黃呢？<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins>你盡力搵哂你可以用錢既地方有無黃店未？</ins></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多apps咁多文宣咁多渠道<br />\n再唔係問下身邊朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一定要攪清楚 要係有選擇之下揀黃 無選擇惟有照奶住先囉</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都可以同時set埋補償機制<br />\n去左一次中立幫襯就要on top of本身目標再去多一次黃<br />\n去左一次藍就要去十次etc.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>此外 推而廣之 你仲可以幫人同佢自己鬥黃</strong></span></span><br />\n留意多d身邊親友有咩成日regular要用錢既地方<br />\n幫佢搵定黃店！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好簡單 例如洗車/補習/換眼鏡/剪髮/買衫/零食<br />\n幫佢搵資料！鼓勵佢地用！氹佢地用！<br />\n「我個fd介紹」「我老婆介紹」「我去過幾好喎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>大家方便都可以係下面留低有咩冷門小店需要支持</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmt4Evy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmt4Evy.gif&h=0ddbe820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeee74648ab6ffa6d23d63e93a5380e0eb887a55","tid":2119474,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"4425864b4d6d2a2cd1c1785201b7e8fb9071245b","tid":2119474,"uid":55493,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"每人每日黃少少"},{"pid":"7c26c92d04f4b39b3348ae673ea32bcfda016aeb","tid":2119474,"uid":10881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"616 之類HOTPOT, <br />\n居酒屋之類晚市鋪<br />\n大家加油頂住佢地"},{"pid":"e39a7eef8b3623f0a4796cc2340b5a1e2023e60b","tid":2119474,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4425864b4d6d2a2cd1c1785201b7e8fb9071245b","tid":2119474,"uid":55493,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"每人每日黃少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"我鍾意你呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370fe6e39938cb83922ce4e1f61f975f9f3a0459","tid":2119474,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c26c92d04f4b39b3348ae673ea32bcfda016aeb","tid":2119474,"uid":10881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"616 之類HOTPOT, <br />\n居酒屋之類晚市鋪<br />\n大家加油頂住佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"外賣！！"},{"pid":"d090982440989adb076c628fa2080a7fb8994b84","tid":2119474,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"be370eb2c694e8d0517eacbe100b933007562178","tid":2119474,"uid":105995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:29:00.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好有同人鬥嘅心"},{"pid":"07a8de914a663c774b13de6078b0670f284beb2b","tid":2119474,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:32:20.